text: Zielone may refer to the following places in Poland: *Zielone, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Zielone, Podlaskie Voivodeship (north-east Poland) *Zielone, Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Zielone, Lublin Voivodeship (east Poland) *Zielone, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship (north Poland)
title: Zielone
